        Leafwhisper says, "Hello! You must be Kira! I'm Leafwhisper! So excited to meet you — we don't get many human travelers — actually, this is my first human — very interesting species — I've been reviewing your documentation — nutritional requirements are fascinating, quite different from standard plant metabolism — the guides in other territories are already preparing compatible compounds — and I understand you're heading to Elder Heartwood, which is such an important journey —"

        Rootwalker cuts in — deep and slow:

        Rootwalker says, "Leafwhisper — let her respond."
